     C*
     C*==< DISPLAY >==*    _____________
     C                     EXFMTECSPW902
     C*                    ~~~~~~~~~~~~~
     C                     TIME           S@TIME
     C*
     C*==< NEXT PROCESSING >==*
S----C                     SELEC
+----C           *IN03     WHEQ '1'                        < F3 >
|    C                     MOVEL'EDT1'    S@PROC
|    C*
+----C           *IN05     WHEQ '1'                        < F5 >
|I---C           D#UPKB    IFEQ '0'
||   C                     MOVEL'DATA'    S@PROC
|+---C                     ELSE
||   C                     MOVEL'CHK2'    S@PROC
|E---C                     ENDIF
|    C*
+----C                     OTHER                           < ENTER >
|    C                     MOVEL'CHK2'    S@PROC
E----C                     ENDSL
     C*
