     C*
     C                     MOVELD#KAT1    K@KAT1            DIE NO.1
     C                     MOVELD#KAT2    K@KAT2            DIE NO.2
     C                     MOVELD#KAT3    K@KAT3            DIE NO.3
     C                     MOVELD#KAT4    K@KAT4            DIE NO.4
     C                     MOVEL'R'       F@PP90
