     C*
     C*==< CLEAR >==*
     C                     SETON                     70
     C*                    _____________
     C                     WRITEECSPW90C
     C*                    ~~~~~~~~~~~~~
     C                     SETOF                     70
     C                     Z-ADD*ZERO     #RRN1
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    D#SMSG
     C                     SETOF                     99
     C*
     C*==< ARRAY SET >==*
     C                     Z-ADD*ZERO     J
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    @DIE
     C                     Z-ADD*ZERO     @RQT
     C*
D----C           *IN92     DOWEQ'0'
|    C           J         ANDLT68
|    C                     ADD  1         J
|    C                     MOVEL*BLANK    W@DIE@
|    C                     MOVELE9KAT1    W@DIK1
|    C                     MOVELE9KAT2    W@DIK2
|    C                     MOVELE9KAT3    W@DIK3
|    C                     MOVELE9KAT4    W@DIK4
