|E---C                     ENDIF
|I---C           E9KAT3    IFNE *BLANK
||   C                     MOVEL'-'       W@DIH3
|E---C                     ENDIF
|I---C           E9KAT4    IFNE *BLANK
||   C                     MOVEL'-'       W@DIH4
|E---C                     ENDIF
|    C                     MOVELW@DIE@    @DIE,J
|    C                     Z-ADDE9REQT    @RQT,J
|    C*                    __________
|    C                     EXSR #PP90
|    C*                    ~~~~~~~~~~
E----C                     ENDDO
     C                     Z-ADDJ         S@MAXJ
     C*
